==Russian==

===Etymology===
Deliberate misspelling of Russian [[по-]] ("a bit") + [[дно]] ("bottom") + the diminutive suffix '''-ок''', plural '''-ки'''.

===Noun===
'''падонки''' (padónki) {{m}} {{p}}

#[[w:Padonki|padonki]] (Internet [[riff-raff]], a Russian-speaking Internet subculture that employs alternative spellings for comic effect, and which delights in the use of profanity and obscene subjects.)

